{"tid":2129754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家千祈唔好買依款口罩！","createTime":"2020-07-28T22:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T07:39:51.000Z","uid":304682,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c72d5996ba3faa3909474acc804e51b12b21ccdc","tid":2129754,"uid":304682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T22:26:57.000Z","msg":"就係呢款君醫口罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4RyGxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4RyGxb.jpg&h=f10c6c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朋友親身經歷<br />\n<br />\n佢之前係呢個牌子嘅口罩廠做過一排，<br />\n口罩獨立包裝好似好衛生<br />\n但係實際上係由<strong>唔知邊到送嚟</strong>一包包嘅口罩重新由人手pack入袋<br />\n而廠內環境極其污糟，啲口罩跌過落地照樣pack<br />\nQC同樣求求其其望一望就算<br />\n有趣嘅係，雖然廠內要求員工戴口罩（多數戴個布口罩就算），但係個老細會唔戴口罩行嚟行去<br />\n<br />\n所以各位買左依款口罩最好都唔好用，未買嘅千祈唔好買<br />\n同埋提下身邊嘅人依款口罩有伏"},{"pid":"3f104998627c1e8df656a27768c3685e7cc9be25","tid":2129754,"uid":6845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T22:28:17.000Z","msg":"咁都要俾d 證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8289debe5edf36cb497fd76838368780d533fa","tid":2129754,"uid":270889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T22:33:42.000Z","msg":"朋友親身證實： 樓主9up"},{"pid":"dc0c3f3c76dca5c48db414018313f4898907dd77","tid":2129754,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T23:19:47.000Z","msg":"無寫VFE就唔會考慮"},{"pid":"f96139c8c4fdb1eda7ae6a951588b50fe29b87eb","tid":2129754,"uid":304682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f104998627c1e8df656a27768c3685e7cc9be25","tid":2129754,"uid":6845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T22:28:17.000Z","msg":"咁都要俾d 證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T23:55:25.000Z","msg":"無證據都無計，因為朋友都好難話影相出嚟<br />\n<br />\n依個post都係旨在提下大家，信唔信就自己嘅事"},{"pid":"b816791c9d0cd7f6bf46b4d0f2e114bfcb94dbf6","tid":2129754,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c